src:
Kåret til et av verdens kuleste nabolag: Hipsterkultur og lokalmiljø i Peckham, London
01 Nov 2019, 09:02 by Marianne Wie
Londons mange bydeler har ofte sin egen identitet og personlighet. Multikulturelle Peckham sørøst i London er eksentrisk, røff og fascinerende.
Stedet er blitt kåret til et av verdens kuleste nabolag av Time Out, magasinet som tar pulsen på London, samt andre byer rundt om i verden.
text:
Named one of the coolest neighborhoods in the world: Hipster culture and the local community in Peckham, London
01 Nov 2019, 09:02 by Marianne Wie
London's many neighborhoods often have their own identity and personality. Multicultural Peckham southeast of London is eccentric, raw and fascinating.
The place has been named one of the world's coolest neighborhoods by Time Out, the magazine that takes the pulse of London, as well as other cities around the world.
